## Benennungs-Konventionen

- **Dateien:** PascalCase fĂĽr React-Komponenten (`CanvasViewport.tsx`), camelCase fĂĽr Utilities/Hooks (`useCanvasRender.ts`, `renderElement.ts`), snake_case fĂĽr Python (`template_set.py`)
